cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.SI

This paper involves computer vision techniques for predicting demographic attributes from Google Street View images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses machine learning approaches, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves crime rates and market research, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) respectively.
